  m_Name: 3.2 Gorinisha
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  botName: Gorinisha
  description: Gorinisha is a native Hinorian who was brought to Jarix by a corporate
    decision of the Spacevoyage company to represent the planet in the Intergalactic
    Championship. This was quite a controversial move both on Hinora and Jarix. Gorinisha
    was not among the best players on Hinora, but was the only one willing to represent
    another planet, as Hinorians are famous for their honor and felt disgusted by
    such a proposition. The native Jarixians are not fans of Gorinisha because in
    their minds he represents all the negative effects that the Spacevoyage company
    has brought to the planet, he is not a native Jarixian but just someone the company
    paid to represent the planet.
  botTexture: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 4da0e430ed0a9d94caea5f25599aaff1, type: 3}
  difficulty: 1
